data.description: This fabulous rustic farmhouse is just absolutely darling! If you are looking for a place to get away from it all then this is it! Situated in the middle of almost 3 acres but feeling like it sits on 30 this home offers seclusion, peace and quiet that's hard to find today! The home features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2191 square feet, a large living room with brick fireplace, and low maintenance cypress siding. Downstairs you will find the large master bedroom and guest bedroom. Upstairs has 2 spacious bedrooms with jack and jill bath. The property has tons of beautiful flowers, loaded fruit trees, pecan trees, and several different varieties of trees (not just pines and oaks).
